video.title: Highlight: Twitch Plays (Viewers play/Chat plays) "Mario Party 3" on a real N64 console, type "!help" to learn how to play

message.body: @cheeseman1230isbackagain Valid inputs are a, b, z, l, r, start, cup, cdown, cleft, cright, dup, ddown, dleft, dright, up, down, left and right. Typos work too! Directions can be replaced with cardinal directions (n, s, w, e, north, south, west, east). Up to 3 buttons can be pressed simultaneously: "b+up+right". End your input with "-" to hold the buttons down for a longer (hold indefinitely until the next input comes) period than normal (266 milliseconds): "a+z+right-". Commands are not case
